      "╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣\n",
      "║  Student         : Aryan Sharma                              ║\n",
      "║  SVM Prediction  : ✅ Pass                                    ║\n",
      "║  Confidence      : 66.8%                                       ║\n",
      "║  Cluster Group   : 📈 Average                                ║\n",
      "╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣\n",
      "║  ── PREDICTION FEATURES (used by SVM)                        ║\n",
      "║  ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────  ║\n",
      "║  Attendance (%)                       72.0        67.0▲   ║\n",
      "║  Assignment Submission (%)            80.0        72.9▲   ║\n",
      "║  Previous CGPA                         6.8         6.7▲   ║\n",
